from solution import Solution

def run_tests():
    s = Solution()
    tests = [
        (5, 7),
        (10, 15),
        (3, 3),
        (1, 1),
        (2, 3),
        (7, 7),
        (8, 15),
        (15, 15),
        (16, 31),
        (31, 31),
        (32, 63),
        (63, 63),
        (64, 127),
        (1000, 1023),
    ]

    ok = True
    for n, expected in tests:
        out = s.smallestNumber(n)
        if out != expected:
            print(f"FAIL: n={n} expected={expected} got={out}")
            ok = False
        else:
            print(f"OK: n={n} -> {out}")

    if ok:
        print("ALL TESTS PASSED")

if __name__ == '__main__':
    run_tests()
